Date			Who		Reason
24 October 2024	navcs2	MTN-33066 EUP - NTO-980 - "89636: Total Weight Should Not be Zero" Error when Uploading Transport Manifest with weights in kilograms only

*/

vars

begin
	return true;
epilog

